test_data_20k = np.array([])

training_data_20k = np.array([])
training_labels_20k =[]
for dir in os.listdir(path_to_dataset):
     for files in os.listdir(path_to_dataset + "/" + dir):
        file_name = path_to_dataset + "/" + dir + "/" + files;
        training_labels_20k.append(files.split('_')[0])
        img = scipy.misc.imread(file_name).astype(np.float32)  # read image and convert to float
        img = img.reshape(-1, 1)
        if training_data_20k.__len__() == 0:
            training_data_20k = img;
        else:
            training_data_20k = np.hstack([training_data_20k, img]);
print training_data_20k.shape

Task 2: 20, 40, 60, 80, and 100 nodes¶

In [97]:
def task2 ():
    experiment = [20,40,60,80,100]
    for n in experiment:     
        model_task2 = Sequential([
            Dense(n, input_dim=784,activation='relu'),
            Dense(784, input_dim=n, activation='linear'),
        ])
        model_task2.compile(optimizer='adam',
                      loss='mse',
                      metrics=['accuracy'])
        all_loss = []
        test_loss = [] 
        #network_l(100)
        for i in range(0,50):
            network = model_task2.fit(new_training_data_20k.T,new_training_data_20k.T, nb_epoch=1)
            all_loss.append(network.history['loss'])
            scores = model_task2.evaluate(new_test_data_2k.T,new_test_data_2k.T)
            test_loss.append(scores[0])
        plt.plot(all_loss)
        plt.plot(test_loss)
        plt.show();

path_to_dataset ='set3_100'
test_data_3 = np.array([])
test_labels_3 =[]
for files in os.listdir(path_to_dataset):
    file_name = path_to_dataset + "/" + files;
    test_labels_3.append(files.split('_')[0])
    img = scipy.misc.imread(file_name).astype(np.float32)  # read image and convert to float
    img = img.reshape(-1, 1)
    if test_data_3.__len__() == 0:
        test_data_3 = img;
    else:
        test_data_3 = np.hstack([test_data_3, img]);
print len(test_labels_3)

pca_values = np.array([])
cov_matrix = np.cov(test_data_2k)
eig_values, eig_vector = np.linalg.eigh(cov_matrix)
index_values = np.argsort(eig_values)[::-1]
top_index_vlaues = index_values[:100]
for top in top_index_vlaues:
    if pca_values.__len__()==0:
        pca_values = eig_vector[top].reshape(784,1)
    else:
        pca_values = np.hstack([pca_values,eig_vector[top].reshape(784,1)])
print pca_values.shape

In [88]:
output_images = model_task3.predict(test_data_2k.T)
pca_values_output = np.array([])
cov_matrix_output = np.cov(output_images.T)
eig_values_output, eig_vector_output = np.linalg.eigh(cov_matrix_output)
index_values_op = np.argsort(eig_values_output)[::-1]
top_index_vlaues_op = index_values_op[:100]
#print eign_vector[0].shape
for top in top_index_vlaues_op:
    if pca_values_output.__len__()==0:
        pca_values_output = eig_vector_output[top].reshape(784,1)
    else:
        pca_values_output = np.hstack([pca_values_output,eig_vector_output[top].reshape(784,1)])
print pca_values_output.shape
